snippet.textDisplay: Gurdas Maan di ki gall ae, sachiyaan kar gya saariyan. Punj daryaavan di dharti Punjab paaven gorryan ne te saaday purkhan ne wundd diti howay, par Punjaabian nu ikk duje tu wakhriyaan karna sokha nae. Lehnday te Charday Punjab di rooh ikk te jind ikk ae, te sada raway gi. Shala Punjab rasda wasda raway, te doway Punjab fer ikk howan. Superb voice, and heartening message given by the legend Gurdas Maan. Jivaay Punjab.
